    Overview

    Meet the EasyFit Sheet, effortless comfort, perfected.


    The Sleeply EasyFit Sheet is designed to solve everything traditional fitted sheets get wrong.


    It goes on in 30 seconds, stays perfectly in place all night, and stays completely wrinkle-free, no lifting, no slipping, no adjusting.

    Made with a silky-soft, breathable fiber blend, the EasyFit Sheet helps regulate temperature and wick away moisture so you stay cool, dry, and comfortable all night long.


    The innovative dual-zone stretch design flexes where you need it and holds firm where it matters, delivering a smooth, hotel-level finish every time you make the bed.


    Simple. Secure. Always smooth.

    Care

    Caring for your EasyFit Sheet is simple.

    • Machine wash cold on a gentle cycle

    • Tumble dry low or air dry

    • No ironing needed, the fabric naturally returns smooth and wrinkle-free

    Wash after wash, it stays soft, breathable, and perfectly fitted.

    Materials

    OEKO-TEX Certified Cover: Hypoallergenic, breathable, and gentle on skin.


    Premium Regenerated Cellulose Fiber Blend

    • Silky-smooth, ultra-soft feel thats gentle on skin and hair

    • Naturally breathable and moisture-wicking for cooler sleep

    • Lightweight, flexible, and designed for all-season comfort

    Dual-Zone Stretch Construction

    • Flexible stretch zones for effortless fitting

    • Reinforced edges for a secure, stay-put fit

    Certified & Skin-Safe

    FAQ

    Is it machine washable?

    Yes. Its fully machine washable and dryer-safe for effortless, everyday care.


    Is it hard to put on?

    Not at all. The EasyFit Sheet is designed to go on in under one minute, no lifting the mattress, no struggling with corners.


    Will it work with deep mattresses or mattress toppers?

    Yes. The flexible stretch design naturally adapts to most mattress depths and toppers while staying snug and secure.


    Will the EasyFit Sheet really stay in place all night?

    Yes. The EasyFit Sheet uses a dual-zone stretch design that flexes for easy fitting while anchoring securely around the mattress. No slipping, no popping corners, no bunching.


    Is it really wrinkle-free?

    Yes. The fabric and construction are designed to stay smooth and crisp without ironing. Your bed stays looking freshly made night after night.


    Does it help with night sweats?

    Absolutely. The breathable, moisture-wicking fabric helps regulate temperature and pull heat and moisture away from your body while you sleep.


    Is it safe for sensitive skin?

    Yes. The EasyFit Sheet is made with gentle, skin-safe materials and is hypoallergenic, making it ideal for sensitive skin.

    Frequently asked questions

    Is it really cool to the touch?

    Yes. FrostWeave fabric uses advanced cooling yarns that instantly draw heat away from your skin. Independent lab tests show it transfers heat up to twice as fast as cotton or silk for a genuinely refreshing feel.

    Does it stay fresh between washes?

    It does. The fabrics odor-resistant fibers and moisture-control weave keep your pillow feeling clean and dry longer, with less buildup from oils or skincare products.

    How is it different from silk or bamboo pillowcases?

    Silk and bamboo can trap heat and require careful washing. FrostWeave offers the same smooth, beauty-friendly surface but stays cooler, feels fresher, and is easier to maintain for everyday use.

    Does it stay fresh between washes?

    Yes. The pillowcase is OEKO-TEX certified, hypoallergenic, and free of harsh coatings. It feels gentle even on delicate or breakout-prone skin.

    Is it machine washable?

    Absolutely. Wash cold, tumble dry low, and it comes out soft and smooth every time. No special care or delicate cycles required.
